1
00:00:07,641 --> 00:00:09,309
Father: POCO, WHERE YOU BEEN?

2
00:00:09,342 --> 00:00:11,678
HOW DARE YOU LEAVE
THE HOUSE LIKE THIS?

3
00:00:11,745 --> 00:00:12,478
( slap )

4
00:00:12,513 --> 00:00:14,480
Poco: BUT PLEASE, PAPA.

5
00:00:14,515 --> 00:00:15,749
( father panting )

6
00:00:15,816 --> 00:00:18,351
Poco: PAPA, I'M SORRY
I LEFT THE HOUSE,

7
00:00:18,451 --> 00:00:20,186
BUT WH‐WHERE'S MY SISTER?

8
00:00:20,286 --> 00:00:22,188
Father: WELL,
WHERE DO YOU THINK?

9
00:00:22,288 --> 00:00:23,690
SHE'S OUT LOOKIN' FOR YOU.

10
00:00:23,757 --> 00:00:25,025
Poco: WHA?!

11
00:00:25,125 --> 00:00:27,093
NO, PAPA. DON'T SAY THAT.

12
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:29,262
TELL ME SHE DIDN'T GO OUT.

13
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:31,865
Father: POCO, WHAT'S AILIN' YOU?

14
00:00:31,932 --> 00:00:33,934
YOU'RE NOT BEHAVIN' RIGHT.

15
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,669
Poco: MY SISTER!

16
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:39,873
MY SISTER!

17
00:00:41,307 --> 00:00:43,443
♪

18
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:52,719
( singing in Japanese )

19
00:02:13,914 --> 00:02:15,381
♪

20
00:02:15,448 --> 00:02:17,116
( sister gasping )

21
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:18,918
( creature laughs )

22
00:02:20,721 --> 00:02:23,624
Dio: CONSIDER THIS, DEAR.

23
00:02:23,657 --> 00:02:26,793
EXAMINE THIS ROSE IN BLOOM
FOR BUT A MOMENT,

24
00:02:26,827 --> 00:02:28,328
VIBRANT, FRESH, AND YOUNG.

25
00:02:28,428 --> 00:02:31,164
WHAT YOU SEE
IS A MIRROR OF YOUR YOUTH.

26
00:02:31,231 --> 00:02:35,168
CONSIDER THIS FACT CAREFULLY,
MADEMOISELLE.

27
00:02:35,268 --> 00:02:38,605
FROM THE FIRST MOMENT
THIS FLOWER FULLY BLOOMS,

28
00:02:38,672 --> 00:02:40,440
IT BEGINS TO WITHER.

29
00:02:40,507 --> 00:02:42,676
A SHAME, DON'T YOU THINK?

30
00:02:42,743 --> 00:02:45,478
Creature: ONLY 16, SO SWEET,

31
00:02:45,512 --> 00:02:47,748
SO INNOCENT AND PURE NOW,

32
00:02:47,814 --> 00:02:50,350
SO FULL
OF DELICIOUS LIFE ENERGY.

33
00:02:50,416 --> 00:02:52,285
WONDERFUL, LORD DIO.

34
00:02:52,352 --> 00:02:53,353
( laughing )

35
00:02:53,419 --> 00:02:54,655
( Dio scoffs )

36
00:02:57,257 --> 00:02:58,792
( creature gags )

37
00:02:58,859 --> 00:03:02,435
Dio: THOSE LACKING IN MANNERS
ARE NOT FIT TO EXIST.

38
00:03:02,503 --> 00:03:04,805
NOW, MADEMOISELLE,

39
00:03:04,871 --> 00:03:07,440
I OFFER UNTO YOU A CHOICE.

40
00:03:07,508 --> 00:03:09,676
WOULD YOU NOT CARE TO ENJOY

41
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:13,379
YOUR YOUTH AND BEAUTY
FOR ALL ETERNITY?

42
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:14,981
FRET NOT, MY DEAR.

43
00:03:15,048 --> 00:03:17,718
I SHALL NOT FORCE
MY FRIENDSHIP UPON YOU,

44
00:03:17,784 --> 00:03:19,185
LIKE OTHERS MIGHT DO.

45
00:03:19,219 --> 00:03:20,954
YOU CONTROL YOUR LIFE.

46
00:03:21,021 --> 00:03:24,525
YOU HOLD YOUR DESTINY
IN YOUR OWN HANDS.

47
00:03:24,558 --> 00:03:25,826
Sister: YOU FIEND.

48
00:03:25,892 --> 00:03:28,729
Dio: EH? HOW'S THAT AGAIN?

49
00:03:28,795 --> 00:03:30,664
( sister gasps )

50
00:03:34,568 --> 00:03:38,204
YOU WEAR THE FLESH,
BUT YOU'RE NOT A MAN.

51
00:03:38,238 --> 00:03:40,574
DEVIL, GO AWAY!

52
00:03:43,409 --> 00:03:44,911
( Dio sighs )

53
00:03:49,583 --> 00:03:52,185
( sister gasps )

54
00:03:52,252 --> 00:03:54,187
( creature growling )

55
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:03,604
Dio: ALAS, ALTHOUGH
YOUR ACQUAINTANCE WILL BE BRIEF,

56
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:06,272
LET ME INTRODUCE MY COMPANION.

57
00:04:08,274 --> 00:04:09,375
( creature growling )

58
00:04:09,442 --> 00:04:12,045
Dio: I PRESENT UNTO YOU DOOBIE.

59
00:04:12,112 --> 00:04:15,448
AS REGRETTABLY
I AM NOT TO YOUR TASTE,

60
00:04:15,516 --> 00:04:17,183
ENJOY YOUR TIME WITH HIM.

61
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:19,352
AU REVOIR, MADEMOISELLE.

62
00:04:21,788 --> 00:04:23,423
( Doobie hisses )

63
00:04:23,456 --> 00:04:26,259
( sister gasping )

64
00:04:26,292 --> 00:04:28,461
( screams )

65
00:04:28,562 --> 00:04:30,463
( Doobie growls )

66
00:04:30,564 --> 00:04:32,132
( sister screams )

67
00:04:32,232 --> 00:04:33,733
( Doobie panting )

68
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,968
( chuckles )

69
00:04:37,537 --> 00:04:39,438
OI! WHO HIT ME?!

70
00:04:39,472 --> 00:04:41,274
WHO'S THERE?!

71
00:04:42,442 --> 00:04:43,877
JoJo: DOESN'T MATTER, DOES IT?

72
00:04:43,944 --> 00:04:45,879
YOU'RE A ZOMBIE.

73
00:04:45,946 --> 00:04:49,249
YOUR KIND DON'T DESERVE
ANY INTRODUCTIONS.

74
00:04:49,315 --> 00:04:50,250
Poco: SISTER!

75
00:04:50,316 --> 00:04:51,818
Sister: POCO!

76
00:04:53,153 --> 00:04:54,955
( Doobie hisses )

77
00:04:54,988 --> 00:04:57,157
( yells )

78
00:04:57,223 --> 00:04:59,225
( JoJo yells )

79
00:05:03,804 --> 00:05:05,772
( Doobie laughs )

80
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,841
BIT YOU. BIT YOU
ON YOUR PRETTY LITTLE FACE!

81
00:05:07,941 --> 00:05:09,943
‐ JoJo: WHAT DID THAT?
‐ Doobie: BIT YOU! BIT YOU!

82
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:11,477
WHAT'S HE GOT UNDER THERE?

83
00:05:11,512 --> 00:05:13,346
Poco: HIS MASK. LOOK AT IT.

84
00:05:13,446 --> 00:05:16,850
( Doobie laughs )

85
00:05:17,918 --> 00:05:19,319
Sister: LOOK OUT!

86
00:05:20,286 --> 00:05:23,624
Doobie: RUN, RUN, RUN.
( chuckles )

87
00:05:23,690 --> 00:05:24,991
( Speedwagon gasps )

88
00:05:25,025 --> 00:05:27,528
THAT ZOMBIE, HE'S CHOCK‐A‐BLOCK
WITH SERPENTS,

89
00:05:27,594 --> 00:05:31,532
ALL SORTS, VENOMOUS COBRAS,
FLESH‐EATING ASPS AND VIPERS.

90
00:05:31,598 --> 00:05:33,967
Doobie: BIT SURPRISED, ARE YOU?

91
00:05:34,034 --> 00:05:36,670
Poco: THEY SANK THEIR FANGS
IN HIS FACE,

92
00:05:36,703 --> 00:05:38,672
AND MORE THAN JUST ONCE.

93
00:05:38,705 --> 00:05:40,206
( Doobie roars )

94
00:05:40,306 --> 00:05:41,542
JoJo: HOW WEARISOME.

95
00:05:41,608 --> 00:05:42,876
I HAVEN'T THE TIME

96
00:05:42,976 --> 00:05:45,712
TO DEAL WITH ANY MORE
OF DIO'S FOOLISH GAMES.

97
00:05:52,886 --> 00:05:55,288
Dire: DAMN. VERY WELL DONE.

98
00:05:55,355 --> 00:05:58,458
HE SQUEEZED OUT THE POISON.
GOOD CONTROL.

99
00:05:58,525 --> 00:06:00,701
HE'S LEARNED A GREAT DEAL
ABOUT BLOOD FLOW

100
00:06:00,734 --> 00:06:02,335
IN A VERY SHORT AMOUNT OF TIME.

101
00:06:02,402 --> 00:06:04,805
Speedwagon: BARON ZEPPELI,
HE'S HELPIN' OUR BOY

102
00:06:04,871 --> 00:06:07,974
AFTER GIVING JONATHAN
HIS LIFE ENERGY WHEN HE DIED.

103
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:13,179
JoJo: I'LL USE A BIT
OF THE GREAT HAMON I POSSESS

104
00:06:13,246 --> 00:06:15,749
TO TURN THESE SERPENTS
BACK ON THEIR MASTER.

105
00:06:18,985 --> 00:06:21,087
( Doobie screaming )

106
00:06:22,889 --> 00:06:23,890
Poco: SISTER!

107
00:06:23,924 --> 00:06:24,891
Sister: POCO!

108
00:06:24,925 --> 00:06:25,926
Poco: SISTER!

109
00:06:25,992 --> 00:06:28,061
( both laughing )

110
00:06:28,094 --> 00:06:30,430
♪

111
00:06:35,769 --> 00:06:37,504
( Speedwagon grunts )

112
00:06:37,571 --> 00:06:39,039
( JoJo grunts )

113
00:06:46,346 --> 00:06:48,381
( footsteps )

114
00:06:48,448 --> 00:06:50,383
♪

115
00:06:55,956 --> 00:06:57,357
( Dio gasps )

116
00:06:59,593 --> 00:07:02,969
JoJo: GUESS WHO SURVIVED
HIS TIME IN HELL, DIO.

117
00:07:03,036 --> 00:07:05,639
Dio: YOU ARE ALIVE, JOJO.

118
00:07:05,739 --> 00:07:07,874
CURIOUS.

119
00:07:07,941 --> 00:07:10,143
I SUPPOSE LOGICALLY

120
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:13,747
THAT WOULD THEN INDICATE
YOU HAVE KILLED MY TWO KNIGHTS.

121
00:07:13,814 --> 00:07:16,149
Creature: LORD DIO,
WE AWAIT YOUR ORDER

122
00:07:16,249 --> 00:07:18,752
TO REDUCE HIM
TO A PILE OF BLOODY FLESH.

123
00:07:18,819 --> 00:07:22,422
Creature #2: LORD, LET MY FANGS
MAKE AN IMPRESSION ON HIM.

124
00:07:22,488 --> 00:07:23,423
JoJo: DIO!

125
00:07:23,489 --> 00:07:24,725
Dio: NO.

126
00:07:24,791 --> 00:07:26,459
THIS ONE IS FOR ME.

127
00:07:26,492 --> 00:07:29,329
HE FALLS BY MY HAND ALONE.

128
00:07:30,731 --> 00:07:32,833
DON'T MISUNDERSTAND ME, JOJO.

129
00:07:33,767 --> 00:07:35,636
HONESTLY THIS IS SOMETHING

130
00:07:35,669 --> 00:07:37,904
IN WHICH I WILL TAKE
NO PLEASURE.

131
00:07:37,971 --> 00:07:40,006
WE WERE RAISED
IN THE SAME HOUSE,

132
00:07:40,073 --> 00:07:42,776
AND THE PROSPECT OF TURNING YOU
INTO AN UNDEAD THING

133
00:07:42,843 --> 00:07:44,745
IS NOT A HAPPY ONE FOR ME.

134
00:07:44,811 --> 00:07:46,079
THAT'S WHY I WANTED YOU

135
00:07:46,146 --> 00:07:48,014
TO BE QUICKLY DISPATCHED
BY MY KNIGHTS.

136
00:07:48,114 --> 00:07:49,182
( JoJo breathes deeply )

137
00:07:49,249 --> 00:07:51,451
Dio: BUT IT WOULD SEEM,
IN THE END,

138
00:07:51,518 --> 00:07:53,920
I UNDERESTIMATED YOU.

139
00:07:53,987 --> 00:07:55,956
SEEING YOU HERE ALIVE

140
00:07:56,022 --> 00:07:57,591
BRINGS ME TO THE REALIZATION

141
00:07:57,658 --> 00:08:01,434
THAT, AS AN EMPEROR,
I WAS BEING FAR TOO SOFT.

142
00:08:01,502 --> 00:08:04,470
BUT NOW,
NOW I'LL PUT YOU TO DEATH

143
00:08:04,538 --> 00:08:06,840
WITHOUT A MOMENT'S THOUGHT
OR COMPUNCTION.

144
00:08:06,873 --> 00:08:08,374
JoJo: I COULD SAY THE SAME.

145
00:08:08,474 --> 00:08:11,477
I WILL FEEL NO HINT OF GUILT
FOR YOUR DEATH.

146
00:08:11,545 --> 00:08:14,615
Dio: BUT FIRST
I HAVE A QUESTION, JOJO.

147
00:08:14,681 --> 00:08:18,685
WHATEVER HAPPENED TO THAT
MUSTACHIOED CHARLATAN OF YOURS?

148
00:08:18,719 --> 00:08:20,486
YOU SEEM TO HAVE LOST HIM.

149
00:08:20,554 --> 00:08:21,855
JoJo: HEAR ME, DIO.

150
00:08:21,888 --> 00:08:23,890
IT SHAMES ME
AS A GENTLEMAN TO SAY THIS,

151
00:08:23,990 --> 00:08:25,992
BUT I CAN NO LONGER
HOLD BACK THE TRUTH.

152
00:08:26,059 --> 00:08:29,830
I, JONATHAN JOESTAR,
HAVE SUCH HATRED FOR YOU,

153
00:08:29,896 --> 00:08:32,065
VENGEANCE CONSUMES ME.

154
00:08:32,165 --> 00:08:34,334
I SWEAR I WILL KILL YOU!

155
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:36,570
( Dio chuckles )

156
00:08:36,637 --> 00:08:39,072
COME, JOJO!

157
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:46,346
♪

158
00:08:46,412 --> 00:08:48,414
COME, JOJO!

159
00:08:48,515 --> 00:08:51,051
( JoJo yells )

160
00:08:52,986 --> 00:08:54,187
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

161
00:08:54,254 --> 00:08:56,590
Dire: JOJO, PLEASE STEP ASIDE.

162
00:08:56,657 --> 00:08:58,091
I HAVE A PRIOR CLAIM.

163
00:08:58,191 --> 00:09:01,001
IT IS MY RIGHT
TO AVENGE MY FRIEND'S KILLING.

164
00:09:01,067 --> 00:09:04,037
ZEPPELI WAS A BRAVE MAN
AND BOON COMPANION

165
00:09:04,104 --> 00:09:07,373
THROUGH TWO DECADES
OF HARSH TRAINING.

166
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,542
DIO, FOR HIS LIFE,

167
00:09:08,609 --> 00:09:12,112
I SHALL NOW SEND YOU
TO THE BOWELS OF HELL ITSELF.

168
00:09:12,178 --> 00:09:14,280
JoJo: NO. WAIT, DIRE.
LISTEN TO ME.

169
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:17,618
DIO HAS HIDDEN ABILITIES
FOR WHICH YOU ARE NOT PREPARED.

170
00:09:17,718 --> 00:09:18,619
( gasps )

171
00:09:20,386 --> 00:09:22,789
Dio: HMM? AH.

172
00:09:22,889 --> 00:09:25,959
THERE'S AN INTERESTING WALK.

173
00:09:26,059 --> 00:09:29,062
APPARENTLY WITH DECADES
OF THE PROPER TRAINING,

174
00:09:29,129 --> 00:09:30,797
MERE HUMANS
CAN ENABLE THEMSELVES

175
00:09:30,897 --> 00:09:32,298
TO FLOAT THROUGH THE AIR.

176
00:09:32,365 --> 00:09:34,768
BUT IN ONLY A SINGLE NIGHT,

177
00:09:34,801 --> 00:09:38,972
I ATTAINED POWER FAR SURPASSING
THAT OF ANY HUMAN GURU.

178
00:09:41,474 --> 00:09:43,443
( laughs )

179
00:09:43,476 --> 00:09:46,813
YOU TRULY THINK YOU CAN
DEFEAT ME IN THIS MANNER,

180
00:09:46,913 --> 00:09:48,381
LIKE YOU WERE SLEEPWALKING?

181
00:09:48,448 --> 00:09:51,317
( yells )

182
00:09:51,417 --> 00:09:53,319
( gasps )

183
00:09:53,419 --> 00:09:55,756
Dire: FELL FOR IT,
DIDN'T YOU, FOOL?

184
00:09:55,822 --> 00:09:59,425
THUNDER CROSS SPLIT ATTACK!

185
00:09:59,492 --> 00:10:01,602
Speedwagon: UNCANNY.
IN CROSSING HIS ARMS,

186
00:10:01,702 --> 00:10:03,103
HE CAN MOUNT AN ATTACK

187
00:10:03,169 --> 00:10:05,772
WHILE STILL KEEPING
HIS GUARD UP FOR PROTECTION,

188
00:10:05,839 --> 00:10:07,273
AN INCREDIBLE STRATEGY.

189
00:10:07,373 --> 00:10:10,577
Straizo: NO FIGHTER HAS EVER
BEEN ABLE TO ESCAPE THIS MOVE.

190
00:10:10,611 --> 00:10:13,046
♪

191
00:10:17,784 --> 00:10:18,952
( all gasp )

192
00:10:19,019 --> 00:10:20,286
Speedwagon: OH, NO!

193
00:10:20,386 --> 00:10:23,423
Dio: USELESS! USELESS!
USELESS! USELESS!

194
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:26,259
Dire: I CAN'T‐‐I CAN'T MOVE.

195
00:10:26,292 --> 00:10:28,461
( JoJo gasps )
HE FROZE DIRE.

196
00:10:28,529 --> 00:10:30,296
Speedwagon: DIO MUST
HAVE SOMEHOW CHILLED

197
00:10:30,396 --> 00:10:32,699
ALL THE MOISTURE
IN HIS BODY AT ONCE,

198
00:10:32,766 --> 00:10:34,434
TURNING HIM TO ICE
IN AN INSTANT.

199
00:10:34,467 --> 00:10:37,237
DIRE CAN'T CONTROL HIS HAMON.

200
00:10:37,303 --> 00:10:40,807
HE CAN'T SEND IT INTO DIO
UNLESS HIS BLOOD IS FLOWING.

201
00:10:40,907 --> 00:10:44,310
'STREWTH, THAT DIO'S A FEARSOME
CREATURE RIGHT ENOUGH.

202
00:10:44,410 --> 00:10:47,648
HE FROZE DIRE'S WHOLE BODY
AT ONCE.

203
00:10:47,748 --> 00:10:50,050
Dire: HOW DID YOU DO THIS?

204
00:10:50,116 --> 00:10:52,285
Dio: OH, WE ARE FEEBLE,
AREN'T WE?

205
00:10:52,318 --> 00:10:55,656
YOU IMBECILE, YOU DARE THINK
YOU COULD LAY A FINGER ON ME?!

206
00:10:55,722 --> 00:10:57,123
( laughs )

207
00:10:57,157 --> 00:10:59,593
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S GOING
TO GIVE UP YOUR LIFE

208
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:01,134
LIKE SOME MONGREL.

209
00:11:01,167 --> 00:11:04,738
LET'S ENDEAVOR TO GIVE THEM
A GOOD SHOW, SHALL WE?

210
00:11:04,805 --> 00:11:07,641
‐ Straizo: NO. DIRE, NO!
‐ JoJo: DIO, STOP IT NOW!

211
00:11:07,674 --> 00:11:11,845
( Dire screams )

212
00:11:11,912 --> 00:11:14,014
( all gasp )

213
00:11:15,516 --> 00:11:17,183
( JoJo gasps )

214
00:11:17,283 --> 00:11:19,419
Dio: IT'S TIME, JOJO.

215
00:11:19,485 --> 00:11:22,923
YOU'RE THE NEXT
I SHALL DISPATCH TO OBLIVION.

216
00:11:22,989 --> 00:11:25,425
( Dire growls )

217
00:11:27,127 --> 00:11:28,161
( JoJo gasps )

218
00:11:28,194 --> 00:11:29,195
Straizo: DIRE!

219
00:11:29,295 --> 00:11:30,831
( Dire chuckles )

220
00:11:30,864 --> 00:11:34,535
THOSE HAMON‐FILLED ROSE'S THORNS
DO STING A BIT.

221
00:11:34,601 --> 00:11:36,770
( chuckles )

222
00:11:36,837 --> 00:11:38,138
‐ Straizo: DIRE!
‐ JoJo: DIRE!

223
00:11:38,204 --> 00:11:40,140
( Dio growls )

224
00:11:40,206 --> 00:11:42,142
INSECT. HOW DARE‐‐

225
00:11:42,208 --> 00:11:44,177
HOW DARE YOU WOUND ME,

226
00:11:44,210 --> 00:11:45,879
WOUND MY FACE?!

227
00:11:45,979 --> 00:11:47,714
JoJo: DIRE, NO.

228
00:11:47,814 --> 00:11:51,552
( sputters )

229
00:11:51,618 --> 00:11:52,886
SPEEDWAGON, MY SWORD.

230
00:11:52,986 --> 00:11:53,887
Speedwagon: CATCH!

231
00:11:53,987 --> 00:11:56,723
♪

232
00:11:56,823 --> 00:11:57,991
JoJo: DIO!

233
00:11:58,058 --> 00:12:00,834
I KNOW EXACTLY
HOW TO DEAL WITH YOU.

234
00:12:00,901 --> 00:12:02,703
DIRE GAVE UP HIS LIFE,

235
00:12:02,736 --> 00:12:05,138
WHICH SHOWED ME
JUST HOW VULNERABLE YOU ARE.

236
00:12:05,205 --> 00:12:07,307
IT WILL BE VERY EASY FOR ME NOW.

237
00:12:07,373 --> 00:12:09,075
YOU WON'T BE ABLE TO STOP IT.

238
00:12:09,142 --> 00:12:10,577
ALL I NEED TO DO IS FILL

239
00:12:10,677 --> 00:12:12,979
BLUEFORD'S SWORD OF LUCK
AND PLUCK WITH HAMON

240
00:12:13,046 --> 00:12:14,515
AND SLICE YOU WITH IT.

241
00:12:16,517 --> 00:12:18,752
( Dio gasps )

242
00:12:20,654 --> 00:12:24,257
Dio: YOU DARE TO TOUCH ME,
FILTHY HUMAN?

243
00:12:24,324 --> 00:12:27,060
YOU DARE TO TOUCH ME
WITH YOUR HAMON,

244
00:12:27,093 --> 00:12:29,763
MORE DISGUSTING
THAN FROG URINE?!

245
00:12:29,863 --> 00:12:31,865
YOUR STRING OF LUCK'S RUN OUT.

246
00:12:31,932 --> 00:12:33,499
( hisses )

247
00:12:33,567 --> 00:12:37,103
NOW SHALL YOU BE FODDER
FOR MY ZOMBIES.

248
00:12:37,170 --> 00:12:39,606
THEY WILL GNAW THE FACES
RIGHT OFF YOUR SKULLS.

249
00:12:39,673 --> 00:12:42,242
Speedwagon: NOW WE SEE.
HE SHOWS HIS TRUE COLORS

250
00:12:42,275 --> 00:12:44,711
AS SOMEONE FIT ONLY
TO RULE OVER A DUNG HEAP.

251
00:12:44,778 --> 00:12:49,115
HIS COOL TOFF'S SOPHISTICATION,
NOTHING BUT A CHEAP MASK.

252
00:12:49,182 --> 00:12:53,119
NOW THAT HE'S HAD HIMSELF A NICE
HUMILIATING TASTE OF HAMON,

253
00:12:53,219 --> 00:12:56,122
HE REVEALS
HIS TRUE FILTHY SELF.

254
00:12:56,222 --> 00:12:58,792
‐ ( zombies growling )
‐ ( both gasping )

255
00:12:58,859 --> 00:13:00,901
Straizo: STRAIZO'S MY NAME.

256
00:13:00,967 --> 00:13:02,235
NO MERCY.

257
00:13:03,436 --> 00:13:05,138
Page: PAGE WOULD BE MY NAME.

258
00:13:05,238 --> 00:13:06,640
Jones: JONES.

259
00:13:06,707 --> 00:13:07,641
Plant: PLANT.

260
00:13:07,708 --> 00:13:08,942
Bonham: BONHAM.

261
00:13:08,975 --> 00:13:11,645
Zombies: NEEDLE VEIN STRIKE!

262
00:13:14,314 --> 00:13:15,916
( zombies yell )

263
00:13:15,982 --> 00:13:18,318
Straizo: ROSES ARE
ALIVE AND VITAL,

264
00:13:18,384 --> 00:13:20,153
SO HAMON
WILL REMAIN INSIDE THEM,

265
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,755
FLOWING ALONG
WITH THEIR LIFE FORCE,

266
00:13:21,822 --> 00:13:24,591
BUT THE SAME THING
CAN NOT BE SAID FOR STEEL.

267
00:13:25,491 --> 00:13:28,228
( zombies screaming )

268
00:13:28,294 --> 00:13:30,396
Straizo: IT'S NECESSARY
TO MAKE CONTACT.

269
00:13:30,463 --> 00:13:32,398
( zombies growling )

270
00:13:32,465 --> 00:13:35,101
Tonpetty: A GREAT MANY OF THEM
ARE COMING.

271
00:13:35,168 --> 00:13:39,673
IF YOU WISH,
I SHALL HANDLE THEM FOR YOU.

272
00:13:39,773 --> 00:13:41,742
♪

273
00:13:46,346 --> 00:13:48,949
Speedwagon: FROM ALL
THE INDICATIONS I'VE SEEN,

274
00:13:49,015 --> 00:13:52,753
THAT BLOKE DIO'S
MORE SWIFT THAN ANY LEOPARD.

275
00:13:52,819 --> 00:13:53,787
( Dio hisses )

276
00:13:53,854 --> 00:13:55,822
Speedwagon:
BUT WITH ZEPPELI'S HAMON,

277
00:13:55,856 --> 00:13:57,991
JONATHAN JUST MIGHT KEEP UP.

278
00:13:58,024 --> 00:13:59,425
( JoJo growls )

279
00:13:59,492 --> 00:14:01,768
Speedwagon: THOUGH DIO
IS STRONG ENOUGH

280
00:14:01,835 --> 00:14:05,706
TO PULVERIZE FLESH AND BONE
WITH A FLICK OF HIS WRIST.

281
00:14:05,772 --> 00:14:06,973
FOR THE BOTH OF THEM,

282
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:10,811
IT COULD BE UP TO WHAT HAPPENS
IN THE VERY FIRST MOMENT.

283
00:14:10,877 --> 00:14:12,212
( Dio grunts )

284
00:14:13,379 --> 00:14:15,516
( JoJo grunts )

285
00:14:16,650 --> 00:14:19,152
‐ ( Dio yells )
‐ ( JoJo breathes deeply )

286
00:14:19,219 --> 00:14:22,689
Dio: I WILL SQUEEZE THE LIFE
OUT OF YOU WITH MY OWN HANDS.

287
00:14:22,723 --> 00:14:26,660
JoJo: I WILL CLEANSE THE WORLD
OF YOUR EVIL INFLUENCE!

288
00:14:27,894 --> 00:14:29,062
Dio: WHAT?

289
00:14:29,129 --> 00:14:31,231
HE SNATCHED UP SOME ROSES
WHEN I WASN'T LOOKING.

290
00:14:31,297 --> 00:14:34,735
( growls )

291
00:14:34,801 --> 00:14:36,069
JoJo: COME NOW!

292
00:14:36,136 --> 00:14:37,504
Speedwagon: WAIT. THAT'S GOOD.

293
00:14:37,571 --> 00:14:39,506
HE CIRCLED AROUND TO THE RIGHT.

294
00:14:39,573 --> 00:14:41,174
DIO IS BLIND ON THAT SIDE.

295
00:14:41,241 --> 00:14:42,876
JoJo: TAKE THIS, DIO!

296
00:14:42,909 --> 00:14:44,210
Dio: NO! DAMN IT ALL!

297
00:14:44,244 --> 00:14:45,912
HE KNOWS EXACTLY
WHAT HE'S DOING!

298
00:14:48,515 --> 00:14:51,251
( Dio screaming )

299
00:14:54,988 --> 00:14:56,422
( JoJo yells )

300
00:14:58,158 --> 00:14:59,593
Speedwagon: YES! KILL HIM!

301
00:15:02,402 --> 00:15:04,104
( JoJo yells )

302
00:15:04,204 --> 00:15:07,273
Speedwagon:
HE FINALLY DEFEATED DIO!

303
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:09,610
( Dio sputters )

304
00:15:09,676 --> 00:15:11,277
DEFEATED?

305
00:15:11,377 --> 00:15:12,946
YOU FOOLS.

306
00:15:13,013 --> 00:15:13,947
Speedwagon: OH, NO.

307
00:15:14,014 --> 00:15:15,949
JoJo: I‐I CAN'T MOVE.

308
00:15:16,016 --> 00:15:18,519
I'M FROZEN.

309
00:15:18,585 --> 00:15:20,954
Dio: YOU'RE SO FEEBLE, JOJO.

310
00:15:21,054 --> 00:15:23,056
( laughs )

311
00:15:23,123 --> 00:15:26,960
NOW, WEAKLING, YOU SHALL JOIN
MY OTHER CHILDREN OF THE NIGHT.

312
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:31,131
( heart beating )

313
00:15:31,231 --> 00:15:33,299
I'VE GOT YOUR
RUBBERY LITTLE CAROTID

314
00:15:33,366 --> 00:15:34,935
BETWEEN MY FINGERS.

315
00:15:34,968 --> 00:15:37,237
SO WARM AND SPRINGY.

316
00:15:37,303 --> 00:15:39,405
A STRANGELY PLEASANT FEELING.

317
00:15:39,472 --> 00:15:41,808
JoJo: A‐‐A KICK.

318
00:15:41,875 --> 00:15:44,611
♪

319
00:15:49,282 --> 00:15:51,785
( gasps ) MY LEGS
HAVE BEEN FROZEN, TOO.

320
00:15:51,818 --> 00:15:54,320
Dio: USELESS! USELESS!
USELESS! USELESS!

321
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:56,990
ENJOYING THIS ANGUISH, JOJO?

322
00:15:57,090 --> 00:15:58,592
ONE TINY LITTLE MOVE,

323
00:15:58,659 --> 00:16:02,569
AND THIS DELICATE BLOOD VESSEL
SNAPS IN TWO LIKE A WET RIBBON.

324
00:16:02,636 --> 00:16:06,072
WITH YOUR CAROTID OPEN,
ALL YOUR BLOOD WILL BE MINE.

325
00:16:06,139 --> 00:16:10,176
THEN I SHALL FILL THE VACANCY
WITH MY OWN VAMPIRIC ESSENCE,

326
00:16:10,276 --> 00:16:12,513
AND YOU WILL BE MY THRALL.

327
00:16:12,579 --> 00:16:15,415
Speedwagon: WE HAVE TO HELP HIM.

328
00:16:15,481 --> 00:16:16,683
Dio: ZOMBIES, TO ME!

329
00:16:17,684 --> 00:16:19,419
KEEP THOSE PEASANTS BACK.

330
00:16:19,485 --> 00:16:21,021
I'M RATHER BUSY.

331
00:16:21,087 --> 00:16:24,658
Tonpetty: NOTHING SEEMS TO STEM
THIS TIDE OF ZOMBIES.

332
00:16:24,691 --> 00:16:27,460
Straizo: WE CANNOT
PROVIDE ANY HELP.

333
00:16:27,528 --> 00:16:31,497
Dio: NOW, JOJO, IN YOUR
LAST MOMENT OF FREE WILL,

334
00:16:31,532 --> 00:16:33,867
REALIZE THAT THE VICTORY
WAS MINE.

335
00:16:33,934 --> 00:16:37,103
JoJo: NO, DIO.
YOU'VE NOT WON YET.

336
00:16:37,170 --> 00:16:39,873
YOU'VE MADE A FATAL MISTAKE.

337
00:16:39,973 --> 00:16:41,041
Dio: HOW SO?

338
00:16:41,107 --> 00:16:42,543
( JoJo laughs )

339
00:16:42,609 --> 00:16:45,045
YOU SEE, DIO,
IF YOU FREEZE ME COMPLETELY,

340
00:16:45,145 --> 00:16:48,048
YOU'LL NOT BE ABLE TO CONTINUE
FEEDING ON MY LIFE ENERGY.

341
00:16:48,148 --> 00:16:51,384
THIS MEANS, HOWEVER,
THAT MY HAMON IS UNAFFECTED.

342
00:16:51,451 --> 00:16:54,955
YOU CAN'T BLOCK IT AS LONG
AS I REMAIN PARTIALLY UNFROZEN.

343
00:16:55,021 --> 00:16:58,525
YOUR TACTICS, TO SAY THE LEAST,
ARE SOMEWHAT FLAWED.

344
00:16:58,559 --> 00:17:00,360
( Dio gasps )

345
00:17:00,393 --> 00:17:02,168
HOW LONG HAS THE SWORD
BEEN IN THOSE FLAMES?

346
00:17:02,235 --> 00:17:05,371
THE METAL BLADE IS
CONDUCTING HEAT FROM THE FIRE

347
00:17:05,405 --> 00:17:07,808
FASTER THAN I CAN FREEZE IT.

348
00:17:07,874 --> 00:17:11,077
HAMON IS FLOWING UP THE BLADE.

349
00:17:12,579 --> 00:17:18,318
JoJo: SUNLIGHT
YELLOW OVERDRIVE!

350
00:17:18,384 --> 00:17:19,753
NOW!

351
00:17:19,853 --> 00:17:21,888
Speedwagon: HE'S DONE IT!

352
00:17:21,922 --> 00:17:23,356
HUH?

353
00:17:23,423 --> 00:17:25,058
Tonpetty: NOT EXACTLY CORRECT.

354
00:17:25,091 --> 00:17:28,829
IT'S QUITE EVIDENT THE HAMON
DID NOT MAKE IT THROUGH.

355
00:17:28,895 --> 00:17:30,531
JoJo: MY ARM.

356
00:17:30,597 --> 00:17:33,166
MY ARM IS FROZEN SOLID AGAIN!

357
00:17:33,233 --> 00:17:35,836
I ONLY BRIEFLY
TOUCHED HIS FACE.

358
00:17:35,902 --> 00:17:39,105
Dio: THIS ISN'T OVER, JOJO.

359
00:17:39,172 --> 00:17:41,107
♪

360
00:17:45,045 --> 00:17:49,349
I HAVE TO ADMIT I MUST ADMIRE
YOUR TENACIOUSNESS.

361
00:17:49,415 --> 00:17:50,784
REALLY, I DO.

362
00:17:50,851 --> 00:17:53,419
AND YOUR INGENIOUS USE
OF THE FLAME,

363
00:17:53,453 --> 00:17:56,790
TRULY MARVELOUS EXAMPLE
OF QUICK THINKING.

364
00:17:56,890 --> 00:17:58,925
HMM.

365
00:17:58,959 --> 00:18:00,794
BUT REALLY, JOJO,

366
00:18:00,861 --> 00:18:03,103
AN EMPEROR'S REACH
SHOULD EXCEED HIS GRASP.

367
00:18:03,136 --> 00:18:06,106
JUST A TOUCH ON THE ARM
IS ALL IT TAKES.

368
00:18:06,139 --> 00:18:10,043
I CAN TURN YOUR WHOLE BODY
TO ICE IN TWO SECONDS.

369
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:12,045
( JoJo grunting )

370
00:18:14,214 --> 00:18:17,718
Speedwagon: THE VAMPIRE ESSENCE,
HE SQUEEZED IT OUT.

371
00:18:17,784 --> 00:18:19,119
HE'S NOT DONE.

372
00:18:19,152 --> 00:18:20,754
JONATHAN WON'T GIVE UP.

373
00:18:23,156 --> 00:18:26,993
Dio: REALLY?
THE "LET'S DO BATTLE" STANCE?

374
00:18:27,093 --> 00:18:28,494
YOU'RE NOT SERIOUS.

375
00:18:28,595 --> 00:18:30,931
NO MATTER HOW YOU PREPARE,

376
00:18:30,997 --> 00:18:34,100
HUMAN ABILITY IS
EXTREMELY LIMITED AND FINITE.

377
00:18:34,167 --> 00:18:37,504
YOUR HAMON TRAINING
AVAILS YOU NOTHING.

378
00:18:37,571 --> 00:18:41,742
IT'S USELESS, USELESS, USELESS,
USELESS, USELESS, USELESS!

379
00:18:41,808 --> 00:18:45,478
A MERE MONKEY
CAN NEVER DEFEAT A LION.

380
00:18:45,512 --> 00:18:47,781
IN COMPARISON TO MY POWER,

381
00:18:47,848 --> 00:18:51,518
YOU ARE BUT A MERE MONKEY, JOJO!

382
00:18:51,585 --> 00:18:53,687
JoJo: YOU'RE WRONG!
WITH TRUE CONVICTION,

383
00:18:53,754 --> 00:18:55,488
THE HUMAN RACE
CAN OVERCOME ANYTHING!

384
00:18:55,522 --> 00:18:59,660
LET ME DEMONSTRATE TO JUST WHAT
HEIGHTS A HUMAN BEING CAN RISE.

385
00:18:59,693 --> 00:19:01,502
Dio: DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME.

386
00:19:01,535 --> 00:19:04,004
A ZOMBIE IS ALL YOU'LL EVER BE!

387
00:19:04,037 --> 00:19:05,772
( yells )

388
00:19:05,839 --> 00:19:09,275
( JoJo breathes deeply )

389
00:19:09,342 --> 00:19:11,945
Speedwagon: 'STREWTH!
HIS HAND IS BURNING!

390
00:19:12,979 --> 00:19:15,215
FLAME'S COMING FROM HIS GLOVE.

391
00:19:15,315 --> 00:19:18,519
THAT MIGHT JUST HAVE THE POWER
TO GET THROUGH DIO'S ICE.

392
00:19:18,552 --> 00:19:19,986
JoJo: WHEN THIS BUSINESS
IS DONE,

393
00:19:20,053 --> 00:19:22,155
WHICH ONE OF US
WILL HAVE FALLEN?!

394
00:19:22,222 --> 00:19:24,357
WE'LL FIND OUT, DIO!

395
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:26,693
( yelling )

396
00:19:26,727 --> 00:19:29,329
( Dio yelling )

397
00:19:29,395 --> 00:19:30,496
( all gasp )

398
00:19:30,564 --> 00:19:32,232
Tonpetty: DIO'S BLOCKING JOJO.

399
00:19:35,502 --> 00:19:36,537
BUT, NO...

400
00:19:36,570 --> 00:19:38,505
IT'S BREAKING THROUGH.

401
00:19:38,572 --> 00:19:40,974
♪

402
00:19:45,378 --> 00:19:47,748
( Dio screams )

403
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,055
I'M DISINTEGRATING.

404
00:19:55,088 --> 00:19:56,056
IT CAN'T BE!

405
00:19:56,089 --> 00:19:58,058
( gagging )

406
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,867
THE PAIN. THE BURNING.

407
00:20:00,967 --> 00:20:01,868
I CAN'T‐‐

408
00:20:01,968 --> 00:20:03,870
( gagging )

409
00:20:06,807 --> 00:20:10,210
MY REIGN WAS
TO HAVE LASTED FOREVER,

410
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:14,014
FOR CENTURIES UNCOUNTED BY MAN.

411
00:20:15,048 --> 00:20:18,218
JoJo: YOU HAD
TO BE DESTROYED, DIO.

412
00:20:19,485 --> 00:20:22,556
Dio: I WILL NOT DIE!

413
00:20:23,389 --> 00:20:24,958
( JoJo gasps )

414
00:20:25,025 --> 00:20:26,226
( zombies gag )

415
00:20:26,292 --> 00:20:28,695
♪

416
00:20:34,334 --> 00:20:35,368
JoJo: HOW DID‐‐

417
00:20:35,401 --> 00:20:36,903
HE SHOT ENERGY
FROM OUT OF HIS EYE.

418
00:20:37,003 --> 00:20:39,673
HE CAME
TO WITHIN ONLY MERE INCHES

419
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,575
OF INCINERATING MY BRAIN!

420
00:20:41,675 --> 00:20:43,577
( Speedwagon gasps )
FAR TOO CLOSE.

421
00:20:43,677 --> 00:20:44,911
Straizo: THE LAST ACT.

422
00:20:44,978 --> 00:20:47,681
THE DEMON REFUSES
TO ACKNOWLEDGE HIS DEATH.

423
00:20:47,748 --> 00:20:50,684
Speedwagon: DIO HAS FALLEN
FROM THE PARAPET.

424
00:20:51,685 --> 00:20:54,320
( Dio screaming )

425
00:20:56,322 --> 00:20:58,258
♪

426
00:21:08,274 --> 00:21:09,843
JoJo: DIO.

427
00:21:18,418 --> 00:21:19,520
( Poco gasps )

428
00:21:19,586 --> 00:21:20,521
LOOK! HE FAINTED!

429
00:21:20,587 --> 00:21:21,955
Speedwagon: HE'S WORN OUT.

430
00:21:22,022 --> 00:21:24,625
TOO RIGHT. HE'S BEEN
IN MORE FATAL FIGHTS TONIGHT

431
00:21:24,691 --> 00:21:26,793
THAN A MAN SHOULD HAVE
IN A LIFETIME.

432
00:21:26,893 --> 00:21:28,962
Poco: BUT WHY
WOULD HE SHED TEARS

433
00:21:29,062 --> 00:21:31,097
FOR AN EVIL CREATURE LIKE THAT?

434
00:21:33,299 --> 00:21:34,635
Speedwagon: HE WEEPS

435
00:21:34,735 --> 00:21:36,637
BECAUSE THEY SPENT
THEIR YOUTH TOGETHER.

436
00:21:36,737 --> 00:21:39,573
DIO WAS LIKE A BROTHER TO HIM.

437
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:43,309
BUT AS FOR ME,
I COULD SING A SONG OF JOY.

438
00:21:45,646 --> 00:21:48,081
BARON ZEPPELI,
WERE YOU WATCHING?!

439
00:21:48,148 --> 00:21:49,249
HE DID IT!

440
00:21:49,315 --> 00:21:51,952
JONATHAN JOESTAR DID IT.

441
00:21:53,486 --> 00:21:55,455
DIO IS DEAD.

442
00:21:55,488 --> 00:21:57,991
IT MAY SOUND AN EXAGGERATION,

443
00:21:58,058 --> 00:22:01,234
BUT JOJO
SAVED THE WORLD TONIGHT!

444
00:22:08,308 --> 00:22:10,243
♪

445
00:22:17,017 --> 00:22:20,854
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

446
00:22:20,921 --> 00:22:24,357
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

447
00:22:24,424 --> 00:22:29,596
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

448
00:22:29,663 --> 00:22:31,865
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

449
00:22:31,965 --> 00:22:35,869
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

450
00:22:35,936 --> 00:22:39,673
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

451
00:22:39,706 --> 00:22:41,775
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
OUT OF THE SKY ♪

452
00:22:41,842 --> 00:22:44,044
♪ AND THEY STAND THERE

453
00:22:46,279 --> 00:22:48,515
♪ ONE MILE OVER,
WE'LL BE THERE ♪

454
00:22:48,549 --> 00:22:50,784
♪ AND WE'LL SEE YOU

455
00:22:53,019 --> 00:22:57,290
♪ 10 TRUE SUMMERS, WE'LL BE
THERE AND LAUGHING, TOO ♪

456
00:22:57,357 --> 00:22:59,059
♪ WITH YOU

457
00:22:59,125 --> 00:23:02,035
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE,
YOU'LL SEE ♪

458
00:23:02,068 --> 00:23:06,673
♪ I'LL BE THERE WITH YOU

459
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,875
( vocalizing )

460
00:23:38,739 --> 00:23:40,674
♪

461
00:23:40,741 --> 00:23:42,509
Speedwagon:
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL SIGHT.

462
00:23:42,576 --> 00:23:44,945
Erina: THESE TEARS
THAT I'M CRYING ARE FROM JOY,

463
00:23:45,011 --> 00:23:46,913
JoJo: YOU MUST LEAVE, ERINA.

464
00:23:46,947 --> 00:23:49,382
Erina: I WANT TO STAY LIKE THIS.

465
00:23:49,449 --> 00:23:51,852
Dio: WHERE IS MY BODY?

